    "John Barton": "Micah Allen, L. C. (1976), The Books ofloel, Obadiah, Jonah and Micah NICOT (Grand Rapids: Eerdmans). Hillers, D. R. (1984), Micah, Hermeneia (Philadelphia: Fortress). Mason, R. (1991), Micah, Nahum, Obadiah, OTG (Sheffield: )SOT). Mays, J. L. (1976), Micah. A Commentary, OTL (London: SCM). Wal, A. van der (1990), Micah. A Classified Bibliography (Amsterdam: Free University Press). Wolff, H.-W. (1990), Micah. A Commentary (Minneapolis: Augsburg); German original, 1982. 33- Nahum Roberts, J. J. M. (1991), Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zephaniah: A Com\u00b7 mentary, OTL (Louisville: Westminster/John `[char_John_Ref]` Knox). Mason R. (1991), Micah, Nahum, Obadiah, OTG (Sheffield: )SOT), 56-84- 34\u00b7 Habakkuk Achtemeier, E. (1986), Nahum-Malachi, Interpretation Commen\u00b7 taries (Louisville: Westminster/John `[char_John_Ref]` Knox). Gowan, D. E. (1976), The Triumph of Faith in Habakkuk (Atlanta: John `[char_John_Ref]` Knox). Hiebert, T. (1996), 'Habakkuk', in The New Interpreter's Bible (Vol. 7; Nashville: Abingdon). Robertson,\n0. P. (1990), The Books of Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zepha\u00b7 niah, NICOT (Grand Rapids: Eerdmans). Roberts, J. J. M. (1991), Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zephaniah: A Com\u00b7 mentary, OTL (Louisville: Westminster/John `[char_John_Ref]` Knox). Szeles, M. E. (1988), Wrath and Mercy: Habakkuk and Zephaniah, International Theological Commentary (Grand Rapids: Eerdmans). 35\u00b7 Zephaniah Ben Zvi, E. (1991), A Historical-Critical Study of the Book of Zephaniah, BZAW 198 (Berlin, New York: de Gruyter). Roberts, J. J. M. (1991), Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zephaniah, OTL (Louisville, Ky.: Westminster/John `[char_John_Ref]` Knox). Robertson,\n0. P. (1990), The Books of Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zepha\u00b7 niah, NICOT (Grand Rapids: Eerdmans)."
